---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="FAQ - Engineering Hub">
  <main>
    <h1>Frequently Asked <span class="text-gradient">Questions</span></h1>
    
    <div class="faq-container">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h2>How do I calculate my SGPA?</h2>
        <p>Use our SGPA Calculator tool. Select your semester, enter your grades for each subject, and the calculator will compute your SGPA automatically considering the credit weightage of each subject.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h2>How do I calculate my CGPA?</h2>
        <p>Use our CGPA Calculator tool. Enter your SGPA for each completed semester, and the calculator will compute your cumulative GPA.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h2>How can I access study materials?</h2>
        <p>Navigate to your scheme year, select your branch, and then choose the desired semester and subject. You'll find organized study materials for each unit.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h2>Can I contribute study materials?</h2>
        <p>Yes! Use our Upload Notes feature to contribute. Materials are reviewed before being published to ensure quality.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h2>How often is the content updated?</h2>
        <p>We regularly update our content to align with the latest VTU syllabus and schemes. New materials are added frequently.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    margin: auto;
    padding: 2rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    color: white;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .text-gradient {
    background-image: var(--accent-gradient);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-size: 400%;
    background-position: 0%;
  }
  .faq-container {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .faq-item {
    background: rgba(var(--accent-dark), 0.2);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  h2 {
    color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  p {
    line-height: 1.6;
    opacity: 0.9;
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>